The paper focuses on the analysis of scientific collaboration and knowledge diffusion, which are topics that are commonly studied in the fields of digital libraries (cs.DL), social networks (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and cybersecurity (cs.CYBER). Additionally, the paper uses citation analysis as a methodology, which is a common approach in the subfield of computational social science (cs.SI).
